Class EssentialViewerPublisher

java.lang.Object
  com.enterprise_architecture.essential.importutility.integration.EssentialViewerPublisher

public class EssentialViewerPublisher
extends java.lang.Object

EssentialViewerPublisher is used to export the Knowledgebase containing the ontology for a Protege Project so that it can be sent to the Essential reporting service.
